Configuring message logging for Edge Data Store follows the same procedure as configuring Edge System message logging as a whole.
	
The schema file Storage.Logging.Schema.json is located in:
•	Windows: %ProgramFiles%/OSIsoft/EdgeSystem/Schema
•	Linux: /opt/EdgeSystem/Schema
For more information, see the following topics:
•	Message logging configuration
•	Change logging levels
•	Configure message logging on Windows
•	Configure message logging on Linux
